title: Natalie Cole - Still Unforgettable 2008
description:
This much anticipated release is a timeless collection of popular tracks from the great American songbook, transformed to life with Natalie's beautiful vocal and iridescent flair.

Recorded at the historical Capital Studios in LA and produced by Natalie herself, the album features classics `Walkin' My Baby Back Home' a duet with Nat King Cole, `Come Rain or Come Shine', `Here's That Rainy Day' and `But Beautiful'.

This album won 2 Grammy Awards at this year's 51st annual awards ceremony for 'Best Traditional Pop Vocal Album' and 'Best Instrumental Arrangement Accompanying Vocalist' for the song Here's That Rainy Day, bringing the number of Grammy Awards she has earned to date to nine. (amazon.com)
